sentences.sentence: I just had a super-duper meal in the restaurant.
sentences.translation: 我刚刚在餐厅吃了一顿超级大餐。

sentences.sentence: I have in my possession the super-duper secret printout of the sales figures of a bookstore.

sentences.sentence: I do think this is super duper cool though, especially as I've been working on a thing that USES it.
